==English==

===Etymology===
From  {{term|magic}} + {{term|-ian}}.

===Pronunciation===
*{{IPA|/məˈʤɪʃən/}}, {{SAMPA|/m@"dZIS@n/}}
*'''Hyphenation:''' ma·gi·cian
*:{{rhymes|ɪʃən}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A person who plays with or practices [[magic]].
# A [[spiritualist]] or practitioner of [[mystic]] arts {{i|often derogatory}}.
# A performer of [[tricks]] or an [[escapologist]].
# A talented [[craftsman]] or [[scientist]].
# A person who is an [[enigma]].

